700868f-a.title: Bronx: Duncomb Street - Barker Avenue
700868f-a.text:
Duncomb Street, at the e.E. corner of Barker Avenue, showing three frame houses, all occupying lot No. 13 (block 4627). The big
apartment house faces on Olinville Avenue.
June 16, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
